{"tid":821781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹襲港】石籬一邨天橋頂部被吹走 碎片四散","createTime":"2018-09-16T05:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T05:11:26.000Z","uid":137672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37432fb94d025ed0cc5099a3d49df6095e8017fb","tid":821781,"uid":137672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】「山竹」吹襲本港，為各區帶來強勁風雨，其中石籬一邨一條往怡峰苑的天橋，頂部被強風吹毀，碎片四散。片段上載於Facebook群組「香港突發事故報料區」，見到石籬一邨一條往怡峰苑的天橋，在強風下，頂部有物料被吹走，碎片散落一地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E8%A5%B2%E6%B8%AF-%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC-%E9%82%A8%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%82%E9%83%A8%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%B9%E8%B5%B0-%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87%E5%9B%9B%E6%95%A3-030100166.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%259F%25B3%25E7%25B1%25AC-%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E9%25A0%2582%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%25B9%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E7%25A2%258E%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2595%25A3-030100166.html&d=jJNVZrUw306%2FfPpxK7f1yv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=018cd86c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E8%A5%B2%E6%B8%AF-%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC-%E9%82%A8%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%82%E9%83%A8%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%B9%E8%B5%B0-%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87%E5%9B%9B%E6%95%A3-030100166.html</a>"}]}